            <title>外媒实测 LENOVO 透明手提电脑，外媒：容易打错字</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/lenovo-project-crystal-clear-laptop/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-project-crystal-clear-laptop</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/lenovo-project-crystal-clear-laptop/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:55:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LENOVO Project Crystal]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[联想]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221688</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前我们报道过，LENOVO 在世界流动通讯大会（Mobile World Congress，MWC）展示了一款配备 17.3 吋 Micro-LED 透明显示器的手提电脑，今日外媒《engadget》就上手实测了这部极具未来感的手提电脑。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《engadget》记者测试这部手提电脑时，其第一印象就是 Project Crystal 的萤幕透明令其印象非常深刻。Project Crystal 关机时萤幕看来就是一块微微棕色的玻璃，但一开机萤幕亮起后，「就如战舰般」，非常有未来感。尽管萤幕由多层玻璃制成，仍然无损其纤薄。《engadget》记者引述 LENOVO 表示，未来考虑在萤幕上添加涂层，轻触后就能够变回传统不透明萤幕般。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲萤幕非常纤薄</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-3-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-3-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《engadget》记者表示，Project Crystal 对比其他萤幕来说，其解析度略嫌不足，仔细观看会看见一粒粒像素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227183942-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227183942-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227183942.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-4-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-4-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲明显可见一粒粒的像素</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《engadget》记者表示，Project Crystal 另一个小缺点是其没有实体键盘，改为采用轻触式键盘。虽然其外观非常有型，但由于缺少了触觉回馈，因此很容易打错字。LENOVO 方面回应指未来可依靠人工智能学习用家的打字习惯，再利用这些数据改善打字体验，根据用家手部运动习惯估计用家想打甚么字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《engadget》记者又指，Projecy Crystal 有接口不足的问题，整部手提电脑仅有两个接口，同时其亦表示，不知为甚么手提电脑会产生大量静电，时常有人在触碰 Project Crystal 时被静电电到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/lenovosprojectcrysta-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>尽管如此，Project Crystal 仅属概念产品，尚未有转为零售的计划，本来就是 LENOVO 受 ThinkPad 部门委托，用作探索透明 microLED 面板与 AI 整合的潜力之产品，因此就无须对它太苛刻吧。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.engadget.com/lenovos-project-crystal-is-the-worlds-first-laptop-with-a-transparent-microled-display-230025521.html">engadget</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CGiYGcZVQcM&amp;ab_channel=Engadget">engadget@YouTube</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/16/msi-x-mercedes-amg-stealth-16-review/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】MSI x Mercedes-AMG Stealth 16 联名版电竞笔电，外型超薄 + 极流畅打机体验</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/08/lenovo-legion-go-review/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Lenovo Legion Go　外形　手感　效能　打机体验　散热　特别功能　屏幕　音效开箱评测</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/28/lenovo-legion-9i-first-review/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Lenovo Legion 9i　外形　手感　功能　打机表现　硬件配置初步评测</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/lenovo-project-crystal-clear-laptop/notebook/">外媒实测 LENOVO 透明手提电脑，外媒：容易打错字</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
