        <item>
            <title>iPhone FineWoven 保护套被外媒批评，容易褪色甩皮状况如烂香蕉</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 08:58:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FineWoven]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221662</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 推出 iPhone 15 之时顺势停产皮革手机壳，改为推出新的 FineWoven 手机壳，成为新一代对应 MagSafe 充电的机壳选择。近日外媒《Wall Street Journal》记者 Joanna Stern 就在 X （前称 Twitter）分享其使用了 5 个月的 FineWoven 保护壳，图片可见该保护壳除了满布花痕及出现褪色问题外，更有明显甩皮问题。Joanna Stern 的帖文引来不少 iPhone FineWoven 保护壳「苦主」留言，表示自己的手机壳也有同样问题。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Here it is. My iPhone 15 Pro Max’s FineWoven case. Peeling edges, scratches and browning like a rotten banana.</p><p>An Apple spokesman said that the company’s cases are engineered at the highest standard to protect iPhones.  </p><p>More on this not-so-fine FineWoven case in my newsletter… <a href="https://t.co/cpDc46LpN8">pic.twitter.com/cpDc46LpN8</a></p><p>&mdash; Joanna Stern (@JoannaStern) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoannaStern/status/1761072266639458745?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 23, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有网民表示，其 iPhone FineWoven 保护壳褪色情况非常严重，甚至使其 MagSafe Duo 充电座亦染上了保护壳的颜色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221664" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447-456x580.jpg" alt="" width="456" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447-456x580.jpg 456w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447.jpg 707w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 456px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/Javi_J/status/1761128853223723035">Javi_J@X</a></p><p>网友 @CalumRaasay 表示自己去年 10 月才刚开始使用 FineWoven 手机保护壳，仅仅 4 个月其保护壳就如「战损版」般，边角位严重甩皮，而且保护壳背部花痕密布。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109.jpg 751w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/CalumRaasay/status/1761112842382500230">CalumRaasay@X</a></p><p>@srcshelton 亦在 X 分享自己的 FineWoven 保护壳，表示「这是 Apple 发布过最差的产品，Apple 应该全额退款回收这个保护壳，并向用户道歉」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The appalling state of an <a href="https://twitter.com/Apple?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Apple</a> 「FineWoven」 (e.g. real leather substitute) premium iPhone Pro case after only 4 months of standard real-world use: this product is the worst Apple has even released &#8211; it should be withdrawn and customers should receive a fully refund &amp; apology. <a href="https://t.co/WnyFN2HhPk">pic.twitter.com/WnyFN2HhPk</a></p><p>&mdash; Stuart Shelton (@srcshelton) <a href="https://twitter.com/srcshelton/status/1756331787926544663?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 10, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/JoannaStern/status/1761072266639458745">JoannaStern@X</a>、<a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/people-are-dragging-apples-finewoven-cases-2024-2">Business Insider</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/phones/some-iphone-15-owners-are-branding-apples-new-finewoven-case-its-worst-ever-product">Tech Radar</a>、<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1420955.htm">cnBeta</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/24/ios-17-3-special-features/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 17.3 必学功能　防盗窃 iPhone 保护 + 简单查所有 Apple 产品保养</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/01/ios-17-senior-mode/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 17 老人模式快速设定，超大字简约介面不怕揿错掣</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/apple-car-plan-ends/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 电动车计划寿终正寝   2,000 名员工受影响</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/">iPhone FineWoven 保护套被外媒批评，容易褪色甩皮状况如烂香蕉</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
