        <item>
            <title>NVIDIA 黄仁勋：小孩不应学写程式，学懂如何用 AI 更重要</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 07:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NVIDIA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黄仁勋]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221490</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>最近 NVIDIA 行政总裁黄仁勋公开表示，现代小朋友不需要再学习编写程式，反而应该专注发展其他领域并成为该领域的专家，再交由 AI 解决各式各样的问题。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Jensen Huang, CEO of Nvidia, argues that we should stop saying kids should learn to code. <br><br>He argues the rise of AI means we can replace programming languages with human language prompts thus enabling everyone to be a programmer. <br><br>AI will kill coding.<a href="https://t.co/SxK9twhEby">pic.twitter.com/SxK9twhEby</a></p>&mdash; Dare Obasanjo🐀 (@Carnage4Life) <a href="https://twitter.com/Carnage4Life/status/1761483377365152234?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 24, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p>日前黄仁勋出席于杜拜举行的世界政府高峰会时提及其对编程的意见。黄仁勋认为， AI 发展迅速，现在编程重要性已不如以往。黄仁勋认为，即使 AI 目前仍然属初期发展阶段，编程也不再是重要技能。黄仁勋指，AI 发展日益蓬勃，人类可以专注在更有价值的专业知识，如生物学、教育、制造或农业等，编程可以交由 AI 处理。</p><p>黄仁勋表示，过去 10-15 年来，大部份科技巨头都认为年轻人学习电脑科技及编写程式等技术攸关重要，但在 AI 日新月异的成长下，年轻人已经不再需要学习这些技能。黄仁勋又表示他的工作就是为了创造一个人类不用学习写程式的世界，AI 发展完善的情况下，全世界任何人也可以是程式设计员。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.techradar.com/pro/nvidia-ceo-predicts-the-death-of-coding-jensen-huang-says-ai-will-do-the-work-so-kids-dont-need-to-learn">Tech Radar Pro</a>、<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/tech-industry/artificial-intelligence/jensen-huang-advises-against-learning-to-code-leave-it-up-to-ai">Tom&#8217;s Hardware</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/nvidia-geforce-rtx-4070-ti-super-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】NVIDIA RTX 4070 Ti SUPER    游戏效能快 20% + 轻松超越上代旗舰</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/rtx-video-hdr/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】任何 SDR 影片升级 HDR 实战    NVIDIA RTX Video HDR 适用于全部 RTX 显示卡</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/24/nvidia-rtx-4070-ti-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【开箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 显示卡  16GB RAM 升级版够抵玩</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/">NVIDIA 黄仁勋：小孩不应学写程式，学懂如何用 AI 更重要</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
